---
title: Sweet Potato and Bacon Risotto with Parsley and Almond Drizzle
description: This Sweet Potato and Bacon Risotto is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-potato-and-bacon-risotto-ecbc8c73.jpg
